"WRTT-305ACN_V00", "ESK-H09-8100R RoHS", and a date code :of '''1403''' is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. Like other RTL8881xx SoCs, this device is using the 8 MiB RAM integrated :into the SoC. The Flash may be rather low (<= 4 MiB, possibly 2 MiB).
Per the FCC EUT's MAC label, a DC:FB:02 OUI is presumed :to be used by at least some devices.
===Additional specs, per the FCC manual=== *11ac connectivity for transfer speeds up to 433Mbps *11n support with speeds up to 150Mbps *Dimensions: [[Dimensions::45 mm x 45 mm x 15 mm]] *Weight: [[Weight::19 g]]
